  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "prof"
   },
   "html": "\n社会主義者、日本共産党初代委員長、「平民新聞」「万朝報」記者、小学校教員"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "table",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "lt"
   },
   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"03s.html\">一覧　（サ）</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/redirect?link_code=ur2&amp;tag=click20thcetu-22&amp;camp=247&amp;creative=1211&amp;path=external-search%3Fsearch-type=ss%26index=blended%26keyword=%25E5%25A0%25BA%2520%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%25BD%25A6\" target=\"_blank\">本を入手</a><img src=\"http://www.assoc-amazon.jp/e/ir?t=click20thcetu-22&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=9\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:none !important; margin:0px !important;\"></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　福岡県出身。大阪で小学校教員や新聞記者を勤めるかたわら、小説を発表。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　「万朝報」に入社、家庭や生活の改良を説く。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　対露強硬論が主流の中、<a href=\"../p/ksyusui.html\">幸徳秋水</a>、<a href=\"../p/ukanzo.html\">内村鑑三</a>とともに「万朝報」で反戦論を展開。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　「万朝報」の方針転換で<a href=\"../1903/10taisy.html\">退社</a>。<a href=\"../p/ksyusui.html\">幸徳</a>らと<a href=\"../1903/11hemin.html\">「平民新聞」を興し</a>戦争中も反戦を主張。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　日本社会党を結成、直接行動論を主張、<a href=\"../p/ksen.html\">片山潜</a>ら議会政策論と対立。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../1908/06sekki.html\">赤旗事件</a>で入獄、結果的に<a href=\"../1910/05taigy.html\">大逆事件</a>の難を免れる。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　出獄後、売文社を設立、記事代行業で生活を支え、時期を待つ。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": ""
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　社会主義思想研究・紹介の一方で、普選、労働運動とかかわり運動の拡大を図る。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../1922/07kyosa.html\">日本共産党を秘密結社として結成</a>。初代委員長。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　共産党事件で逮捕、保釈釈放後、共産党を離れ、社会民主主義左派の立場をとる。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
